<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-idp225643904">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-idp4814048">
<p id="fs-idp166353408">Write a balanced equation for each of the following nuclear reactions:</p>
<p id="fs-idp160023024">(a) the production of <sup>17</sup>O from <sup>14</sup>N by &#945; particle bombardment</p>
<p id="fs-idp167819312">(b) the production of <sup>14</sup>C from <sup>14</sup>N by neutron bombardment</p>
<p id="fs-idp163053056">(c) the production of <sup>233</sup>Th from <sup>232</sup>Th by neutron bombardment</p>
<p id="fs-idp25746336">(d) the production of <sup>239</sup>U from <sup>238</sup>U by <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mrow/><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mtext>H</mtext></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><msubsup><mrow/><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mtext>H</mtext></annotation-xml></semantics></math> bombardment</p></div>
<div data-type="solution" id="fs-idp40755120">
<p id="fs-idp233165328">(a) <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow>
